          <h3>圖文資訊</h3>
          <p>Infographics、數據視覺化、懶人包</p>
          <span class="res-cat-count">⚠️ 建置中</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/research-result/download-zone/" class="res-cat-card">
          <div class="res-cat-icon" style="background:rgba(13,148,136,.1);color:#0d9488;"><i class="fas fa-download"></i></div>
          <h3>下載專區</h3>
          <p>簡報、手冊、教材檔案下載</p>
          <span class="res-cat-count">⚠️ 建置中</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/research-result/related-resources/" class="res-cat-card">
          <div class="res-cat-icon" style="background:rgba(124,58,237,.1);color:#7c3aed;"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></div>
          <h3>相關資源</h3>
          <p>政府資料庫、相關計畫、國際文獻</p>
          <span class="res-cat-count">⚠️ 建置中</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== 區塊 3：最新成果精選 ========== -->
<div class="res-sections" id="res-featured">
  <div class="res-sec-card">
    <div class="res-sec-header">
      <div class="res-sec-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
      <div><h2>最新成果精選</h2><p>橫跨各分類的最新產出。</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="res-sec-body">
      <div class="res-feat-list">

        <!-- ===== 精選卡片模板（複製此區塊新增）===== -->
        <div class="res-feat-card">
          <div class="res-feat-type res-type-journal"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i> 研究出版</div>
          <div class="res-feat-content">
            <h3>⚠️ APA 格式完整引用，例如：<br>Wang, Y.-C., &amp; Chen, L.-H. (2025). Occupational health literacy among aging farmers in Yunlin-Chiayi region. <em>Journal of Agricultural Safety and Health</em>, <em>31</em>(2), 145–162. https://doi.org/xxxxx</h3>
            <p class="res-feat-abstract">⚠️ 摘要：50–80 字概述研究目的、方法與主要發現。</p>
            <div class="res-feat-tags">
              <span class="res-feat-tag">⚠️ 關鍵字 1</span>
              <span class="res-feat-tag">⚠️ 關鍵字 2</span>
              <span class="res-feat-tag">⚠️ 關鍵字 3</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="res-feat-actions">
            <!-- ⚠️ 替換 href 為 PDF 檔案 URL -->
            <a href="#" class="res-dl-btn"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> PDF 下載<span class="res-dl-size">⚠️ MB</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- ===== 精選卡片模板結束 ===== -->

        <div class="res-feat-card">
          <div class="res-feat-type res-type-podcast"><i class="fas fa-podcast"></i> Podcast</div>
          <div class="res-feat-content">
            <h3>⚠️ 節目標題，例如：EP.01 — 與雲林稻農的對話：農業職災不該是宿命</h3>
            <p class="res-feat-abstract">⚠️ 節目摘要。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="res-feat-actions">
            <a href="#" class="res-play-btn"><i class="fas fa-headphones"></i> 前往收聽</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="res-feat-card">
          <div class="res-feat-type res-type-infographic"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i> 圖文資訊</div>
          <div class="res-feat-content">
            <h3>⚠️ 圖表標題，例如：雲嘉農民職業健康風險一覽</h3>
            <p class="res-feat-abstract">⚠️ 摘要。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="res-feat-actions">
            <a href="#" class="res-dl-btn"><i class="fas fa-image"></i> 檢視<span class="res-dl-size">⚠️ PNG</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ⚠️ 繼續複製 .res-feat-card 新增更多精選 -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

